sentences: The conclusions on AIJ (FCCC/SBSTA/2002/L.2) recommend a draft COP-8 decision and agree on a revised URF, both of which are contained in FCCC/SBSTA/2002/L.2/Add.1.
The draft decision adopts the revised URF and urges Parties involved in AIJ to use it.
enb_long_title: Sixteenth Sessions of the Subsidiary Bodies
